# Kurush, Khasavyurtovsky District, Republic of Dagestan

}}
Kurush (; ) is a rural locality (a selo) in Khasavyurtovsky District, Republic of Dagestan, Russia.  there are 133 streets.
Geography
Kurush is located 24&nbsp;km northeast of Khasavyurt (the district's administrative centre) by road. Kazmaaul is the nearest rural locality.
